    About this hotel

    Set on a hillside along the NH5 road, this upscale hotel with views of the Himalayas is 4 km from Lakkar Bazar, and 5 km from the bustling Mall Road and Jakhu Ropeway Shimla cable car.

    Featuring mountain views, the warmly decorated rooms offer Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs, plus minifridges and kettles. Suites add sitting areas.

    A polished restaurant features views of the mountains. Other amenities include a bar and a gym. Breakfast and parking are available.

    Check-in time: 14:00
    Check-out time: 12:00
